hosts.about:
A Friend started a relationship with Airbnb a few years ago. He tried to get me involved but I really wasn't interested, but then I found myself always helping him out, greeting guests, doing laundry and keeping his apartment up, he asked me again to join Airbnb, and I said why not, and here I am. 

I am very friendly and outgoing. I love traveling. I love animals.
